rsCssSpritesPlugin
==============

The `rsCssSpritesPlugin` adds a task to generate css sprites from your images and stylesheets.

it uses the smartsprites library (java) from http://csssprites.org


Installation
------------

  * Install the plugin

        $ symfony plugin:install rsCssSpritesPlugin -s beta

Usage
-----
  * prepare your stylesheets and images, see http://csssprites.org/ how to use it

  * run the task

        $ symfony generate:sprites


